EventComponent.Name: I Night Kick-off Dance
EventComponent.Title: I-Night Dance
EventComponent.Abstract: Come meet new friends at I-night. This can't miss, fun-filled, start-of the semester celebration for all BYU-Idaho students. Activities start at 7 p.m. Dance instruction begins at 8 p.m. to 9 p.m. and dance begins at 11p.m. One cost for all events see link.
